entry.title: Ukraine Calls Up Reservists; West Steps Up Sanctions
entry.content: Ukraine’s president ordered the mobilization of reservists as Russian troops poured into Ukraine’s eastern Donbas region. Western nations announced measures to punish Moscow for recognizing two Russian-controlled statelets there as independent.

entry.title: A Real-Life 'Queen's Gambit'---the Brazilian Maid Who Became a Chess Champ
entry.content: Cibele Florêncio worked her way to tournaments; “People look at me and wonder what the hell I’m doing there.”
